  ('heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-00059', 'heelevel3-d592fc58', 'heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '以下為去年臺灣國際收支平衡表內各項目的變動：出口800萬美元、進口700萬美元、資本帳淨 流出100萬美元、本國對外國直接投資300萬美元、外國對本國直接投資200萬美元。在不考慮 誤差與遺漏與其他項目的變動下，去年我國央行準備資產變動為何？', '["增加100萬美元", "減少100萬美元", "增加200萬美元", "減少200萬美元 32260 32760"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "327", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-00060', 'heelevel3-d592fc58', 'heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '某國政府面臨債務危機，如果無法提高債務上限，違約機會就會上升。為避免違約，該國必須增 稅並大量削減財政支出，在短期會產生何種影響？', '["總合需求曲線左移，物價水準下降，實質GDP下降", "總合需求曲線右移，物價水準上升，實質GDP上升", "短期總合供給曲線左移，物價水準上升，實質GDP下降", "短期總合供給曲線右移，物價水準下降，實質GDP上升"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "327", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-00061', 'heelevel3-d592fc58', 'heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '以支出法求算GDP時，下列何者列入政府購買支出？', '["政府公債的利息支出", "失業保險津貼", "政府興建高速公路的支出", "對人民的褔利支出"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "327", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-00062', 'heelevel3-d592fc58', 'heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據李嘉圖均等定理（Ricardianequivalencetheorem），假設其他條件不變，政府暫時性的調低其 定額稅，此減稅對於私部門支出的影響效果：', '["為零", "超過該減稅額", "等於該減稅額", "大於零，但小於該減稅額"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "327", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-00063', 'heelevel3-d592fc58', 'heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', 'A 公司購買了一個新型螢幕用以展示產品，此螢幕的售價為 50,000 元，而該機型的折舊率為每年 25%。假設A公司向銀行借貸的利率為10%、存款利率為6%、預期通貨膨脹率為5%。若A公司利 用自有資金購買此螢幕設備，則A公司第一年的廠商使用資本成本（usercostofcapital）為何？', '["12,500元", "13,000元", "15,000元", "12,000元"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "327", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-00064', 'heelevel3-d592fc58', 'heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為中央銀行最常用來減少貨幣供給的操作方式？', '["提高稅率", "買入政府公債", "在公開市場買入債券", "在公開市場賣出債券"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "327", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-00065', 'heelevel3-d592fc58', 'heelevel3-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '如果貨幣需求受到利率和所得的影響，貨幣需求的所得彈性為2，且通貨膨脹率為2%。假定貨幣 的流通速度與短期利率皆為固定，在實質年經濟成長率為3%時，根據貨幣數量方程式，中央銀行 貨幣供給的年增加率為何？', '["7%", "8%", "9%", "10%"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "327", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
